            <div type="a">
                <column>03</column>
                <head>The Forthcoming Fair</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <transcript>
                    <p/>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Preparations are underway for Franklin County's first fair. Buildings and
                    the "best ever graded" track in the area are under construction. "When we
                    consider the extent and wealth of Franklin county, in agriculture, manufactures,
                    and all that goes to make up a community of thrift and industry, we know we
                    shall have a grand representation of the industry of her citizens, when the time
                    arrives."</summary>
                <note/>
