                <summary>Jacob Bickley died in Chambersburg on August 3rd. He was 80 years old. "The
                    deceased had been regularly admitted into, and died in full connection with the
                    'River Brethren' denomination, a fact not known to, and hence not mentioned by
                    either of the speakers on the occasion of the memorial. He was a man of
                    excellent moral character and genuine religious experience, and no doubt died
                    'in the Lord.'"</summary>
